65
00:05:08,790 --> 00:05:09,990
Walang problema, Dakilang Ninuno.

66
00:05:51,350 --> 00:05:52,190
Huwag kang lalapit sa akin.

67
00:05:52,670 --> 00:05:53,510
Masyado kang madumi.

68
00:06:22,030 --> 00:06:23,910
Wala ka lang

69
