70
00:06:26,060 --> 00:06:27,670
Paano ka nagkaroon ng ganoong kapangyarihan?

71
00:06:29,150 --> 00:06:29,990
Your Grace,

72
00:06:30,230 --> 00:06:31,070
sa totoo lang,

73
00:06:31,910 --> 00:06:32,963
