136
00:10:20,990 --> 00:10:22,380
Twenty ka lang ba talaga?

137
00:10:26,900 --> 00:10:27,780
Sama ka sa akin.

138
00:10:28,830 --> 00:10:29,670
Hindi ka mortal.

139
00:10:31,590 --> 00:10:33,310
Sa totoo lang, wala akong pakialam kung sino ka.

140
00:10:34,830 --> 00:10:35,990
Lumaki na si Fengyi.

141
00:10:36,590 --> 00:10:38,070
Hindi niya kailangan na ako ang magdesisyon para sa kanya.

142
00:10:39,230 --> 00:10:40,070
Kahit ano ka pa,

143
00:10:41,140 --> 00:10:42,362
dapat nasa tabi ka niya

144
00:10:42,373 --> 00:10:43,430
para sa isang dahilan.

145
00:10:45,110 --> 00:10:46,020
Fengyi ay hindi kailanman naging

146
00:10:46,710 --> 00:10:48,310
madaling palakihin ang bata.

147
00:10:49,310 --> 00:10:50,230
Siya ay malalim na curious,

148
00:10:50,900 --> 00:10:51,830
ngunit mahina ang katawan,

149
00:10:52,500 --> 00:10:53,500
sinasaktan ng sakit.

150
00:10:53,500 --> 00:10:54,470
Baka hindi na siya mabuhay ng matagal.

151
00:10:55,990 --> 00:10:57,590
Ang daan sa unahan ay kanyang lakaran.

152
00:11:00,020 --> 00:11:01,380
Sana sa tabi niya lang,

153
00:11:02,660 --> 00:11:03,780
pwede mo siyang bantayan.

154
00:11:24,740 --> 00:11:27,190
Sa Shunzhou horse graft,

155
00:11:27,845 --> 00:11:29,625
Sun Changde,
Registrar ng Imperial Stud,

156
00:11:29,636 --> 00:11:30,706
ay nagbago ng kanyang patotoo.

157
00:11:31,380 --> 00:11:32,500
Inutusan daw siya

158
00:11:32,500 --> 00:11:34,430
para i-frame si Sun Zi'an, Minister of War,

159
00:11:34,590 --> 00:11:36,230
at Li Li,
Ministro ng Imperial Stud.

160
00:11:36,590 --> 00:11:37,710
Ang nag-utos sa kanya

161
00:11:38,230 --> 00:11:41,140
ay si Duan Xu, Court Counselor.

162
00:11:42,230 --> 00:11:43,070
Duan Xu,

163
00:11:43,453 --> 00:11:44,600
may sasabihin ka ba?

164
00:11:46,350 --> 00:11:47,190
Kamahalan,

165
00:11:48,190 --> 00:11:49,030
Wala akong ginawang ganyan.

166
00:11:52,900 --> 00:11:53,830
Kamahalan,

167
00:11:54,620 --> 00:11:57,020
ang horse craft ay talagang festered

168
00:11:57,660 --> 00:11:59,020
sa loob ng sampung taon.

169
00:11:59,860 --> 00:12:01,350
Sa utos ng iyong kamahalan,

170
00:12:01,653 --> 00:12:02,852
Inimbestigahan ko na ang kasong ito.

171
00:12:02,990 --> 00:12:03,830
Ang mga punong salarin

172
00:12:03,830 --> 00:12:05,710
ay si Sun Zi'an, Ministro ng Digmaan,

173
00:12:06,003 --> 00:12:07,669
at Li Li,
Ministro ng Imperial Stud,

174
00:12:08,070 --> 00:12:09,660
hindi ang Court Counselor.

175
00:12:09,900 --> 00:12:10,830
Kaya, ito ay totoo.

176
00:12:11,310 --> 00:12:12,710
Dapat solid ang patunay.

177
00:12:13,110 --> 00:12:14,276
Ayon kay Sun Changde,

178
00:12:14,287 --> 00:12:15,533
Registrar ng Imperial Stud,

179
00:12:15,710 --> 00:12:16,860
ilang buwan na ang nakalipas,

180
00:12:17,070 --> 00:12:18,830
