556
00:34:15,990 --> 00:34:17,060
kaya isinantabi niya ang kanyang pride

557
00:34:17,350 --> 00:34:18,870
at itinanghal ang buong komedya na ito

558
00:34:19,750 --> 00:34:20,910
para mangyari ito sa iyo.

559
00:34:23,390 --> 00:34:25,180
Inayos ito ni Mr. Duan sa akin

560
00:34:25,500 --> 00:34:26,990
para matulungan kami ni Xuan na maisakatuparan ito.

561
00:34:27,660 --> 00:34:28,500
Sabi niya

562
00:34:28,910 --> 00:34:30,140
marami na siyang nakita

563
00:34:30,350 --> 00:34:31,580
ng tinatawag na mutual respect

564
00:34:31,580 --> 00:34:32,500
at pekeng pagmamahal.

565
00:34:32,830 --> 00:34:34,060
Nakita niya itong hindi mabata na mapurol.

566
00:34:35,430 --> 00:34:36,910
Siya rin, may tao sa puso niya.

567
00:34:37,950 --> 00:34:38,870
Sabi niya rin

568
00:34:39,350 --> 00:34:40,750
siya ang babaeng pinakamamahal niya.

569
00:34:41,660 --> 00:34:42,500
Marahil

570
00:34:42,910 --> 00:34:44,350
hinding-hindi siya pakakasalan ng babaeng iyon.

571
00:34:44,790 --> 00:34:45,750
Pagkatapos ay gagawin niya

572
00:34:46,270 --> 00:34:47,910
manatiling walang asawa sa buong buhay niya.

573
00:34:52,180 --> 00:34:53,390
Miss Wang at Xuan

574
00:34:53,390 --> 00:34:54,230
ay umiibig.

575
00:34:55,060 --> 00:34:55,950
Pinasuot kami ni Xu

576
00:34:55,950 --> 00:34:57,100
napakagandang performance.

577
00:34:57,430 --> 00:34:58,660
Tinulungan niya si Miss Wang,

578
00:34:59,020 --> 00:34:59,910
pati na rin ang kanyang sarili

579
00:34:59,910 --> 00:35:01,020
at ang mahal niya.

580
00:35:01,700 --> 00:35:02,580
Dapat mong maunawaan

581
00:35:02,580 --> 00:35:03,500
kanyang intensyon.

582
00:35:23,580 --> 00:35:24,420
Pumunta ka.

583
00:35:25,430 --> 00:35:26,270
Pumunta ka.

584
00:35:27,180 --> 00:35:28,020
nasaan siya?

585
00:35:39,460 --> 00:35:42,580
(Duan Mansion)

586
00:35:42,580 --> 00:35:45,140
(Liham ng Hamon)

587
00:35:45,140 --> 00:35:46,060
Ang nobya

588
00:35:46,060 --> 00:35:48,060
ay dinakip ng mga espiya ni Chong.

589
00:35:49,660 --> 00:35:51,580
Nabalitaan ko kasi si Duan Xu

590
00:35:51,910 --> 00:35:54,660
nakakakuha ng masyadong pansin
sa hilagang larangan ng digmaan,

591
00:35:55,060 --> 00:35:56,870
kaya kinuha ng mga espiya ni Chong ang nobya

592
00:35:56,870 --> 00:35:57,950
para makaganti

593
00:35:58,180 --> 00:35:59,540
at ipahiya siya.

594
00:35:59,990 --> 00:36:01,060
Napakalayo na nila.

595
00:36:01,620 --> 00:36:03,350
Si Mr. Wang ay halos himatayin sa galit.

596
00:36:04,790 --> 00:36:06,540
Ang kanyang anak na babae ang tunay na biktima.

597
00:36:07,310 --> 00:36:08,700
tama yan.

598
00:36:09,830 --> 00:36:10,670
Xu,

599
00:36:10,950 --> 00:36:11,790
paano ito?

600
00:36:12,100 --> 00:36:13,270
Nahanap mo na ba ang nobya?

601
00:36:18,020 --> 00:36:19,310
- Ano ang gagawin?
- Ano ang gagawin natin?

602
00:36:21,060 --> 00:36:22,100
Yung mga espiya ni North Chong.

603
00:36:24,660 --> 00:36:26,060
Yaong mga kawawang espiya ng North Chong.

604
00:36:26,060 --> 00:36:27,140
Sila ay tunay na kasuklam-suklam.

605
00:36:36,990 --> 00:36:38,870
- Mga ginoo.
- Dahil nandito ka,

606
00:36:40,750 --> 00:36:41,830
