609
00:36:51,540 --> 00:36:52,620
at sinaktan ang aking kamag-anak.

610
00:36:53,220 --> 00:36:54,500
Ngayon, kinuha na nila ang aking nobya

611
00:36:54,950 --> 00:36:56,580
