614
00:37:01,620 --> 00:37:03,220
Si Wang, nobya ng Duan clan,

615
00:37:03,500 --> 00:37:04,500
ay banal at banayad.

616
00:37:05,100 --> 00:37:06,580
Ngayon, dinaranas niya ang kalamidad na ito

617
00:37:08,020 --> 00:37:09,950
